<p id="P51">This project was supported by funds from Health Canada’s Genomics Research and Development Initiative awarded to CLY. Stipend support for EC was also provided through the Research in Environmental and Analytical Chemistry and Toxicology (REACT) program funded under the Natural Science and Engineering Council of Canada (NSERC)’s Collaborative Research and Training (CREATE) Program. The information in this document has subjected to review by the Center for Computational Toxicology and Exposure of the US EPA and approved for publication. Approval does not signify that the contents reflect the views of the Agency, nor does mention of trade names or commercial products constitute endorsement or recommendation for use. We would like to thank Rémi Gagné and Dr. Matthew Meier (Health Canada) for their support in data processing and the reviewers Drs. Daniel Desaulniers, Mike Wade (Health Canada), and Brian Chorley (US EPA) for their input on the manuscript.</p></section><section id="glossary1" class="glossary"><h2 class="pmc_sec_title">ABBREVIATIONS</h2>
